Packages that use org.jvnet.ws.wadl
org.jvnet.ws.wadl   
org.jvnet.ws.wadl2java Implements a WADL to Java tool that generates client-side stubs for the resources and methods declared in a WADL file. 
org.jvnet.ws.wadl2java.ast Classes to insulate code generator from JAXB generated classes.
